 word, and its participial derivative 
&lt;mentioned xml:id="X235" xml:lang="el"&gt;lutheis&lt;/mentioned&gt;
&lt;gloss target="#X235"&gt;released,&lt;/gloss&gt; accented on the last.</pre> Content model <pre>
