&lt;standOff&gt; Functions as a container element for linked data, contextual information, and stand-off annotations embedded in a TEI document. [17.10. The standOff Container] Module linking Attributes <ul> <li>att.global<ul><li>@xml:id</li> <li>@n</li> <li>@xml:lang</li> <li>@xml:base</li> <li>@xml:space</li> </ul> <ul> <li>att.global.analytic<ul><li>@about</li> <li>@ana</li> </ul></li><li>att.global.change<ul><li>@change</li></ul></li><li>att.global.facs<ul><li>@facs</li></ul></li><li>att.global.linking<ul><li>@corresp</li><li>@synch</li><li>@sameAs</li><li>@copyOf</li><li>@next</li><li>@prev</li><li>@exclude</li><li>@select</li></ul></li><li>att.global.rendition<ul><li>@rend</li><li>@style</li><li>@rendition</li></ul></li><li>att.global.responsibility<ul><li>@cert</li><li>@resp</li></ul></li><li>att.global.source<ul><li>@source</li></ul></li></ul></li><li>att.declaring<ul><li>@decls</li></ul></li><li>att.typed<ul><li>@type</li><li>@subtype</li></ul></li></ul> Member of model.resource Contained by core: teiCorpus textstructure: TEI May contain analysis: interp interpGrp core: bibl biblStruct list note linking: seg msdescription: msDesc namesdates: listPerson Example This example shows an encoding of morphosyntactic features similar to the encoding system used by ISO 24611 (MAF).<pre>&lt;TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"&gt;
 &lt;teiHeader&gt;
&lt;!-- ... --&gt;
 &lt;/teiHeader&gt;
 &lt;text&gt;
  &lt;body&gt;
&lt;!-- ... --&gt;
   &lt;p&gt;
    &lt;w xml:id="w51"&gt;I&lt;/w&gt;
    &lt;w xml:id="w52"&gt;wanna&lt;/w&gt;
    &lt;w xml:id="w53"&gt;put&lt;/w&gt;
    &lt;w xml:id="w54"&gt;up&lt;/w&gt;
    &lt;w xml:id="w55"&gt;new&lt;/w&gt;
    &lt;w xml:id="w56"&gt;wallpaper&lt;/w&gt;
    &lt;pc&gt;.&lt;/pc&gt;
   &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;!-- ... --&gt;
  &lt;/body&gt;
 &lt;/text&gt;
 &lt;standOff type="morphosyntax"&gt;
  &lt;spanGrp type="wordForm"&gt;
   &lt;span target="#w51" ana="#fs01"/&gt;
   &lt;span target="#w52" ana="#fs02"/&gt;
   &lt;span target="#w52" ana="#fs03"/&gt;
   &lt;span target="#w53 #w54" ana="#fs04"/&gt;
   &lt;span target="#w55" ana="#fs05"/&gt;
   &lt;span target="#w56" ana="#fs06"/&gt;
  &lt;/spanGrp&gt;
  &lt;fs xml:id="fs01"&gt;
   &lt;f name="lemma"&gt;
    &lt;string&gt;I&lt;/string&gt;
   &lt;/f&gt;
   &lt;f name="pos"&gt;
    &lt;symbol value="PP"/&gt;
   &lt;/f&gt;
  &lt;/fs&gt;
